ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Highly, highly recommend it. If you're at all interested in sexuality, health, women's rights, gay rights, human rights, and activism of any stripe, this course is essential.
I would definitely recommend the course to anyone interested in human rights or sexual rights or to any student interested in the overlap of the global public health and human rights systems.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: I was able to apply what I learned in this course to my own research interests and subject area.
